snippet.title: Robin Hood's Quest (PS2) Complete Walkthrough Playthrough Gameplay Full Game
snippet.description:
Robin Hood's Quest full game walkthrough for PlayStation 2 played on a real hardware with no lives lost.

Recorded with Elgato Game Capture HD from a real PS2 console using Component-HDMI Converter that plugs directly into PS2. Game runs at 50 fps PAL standard with no alternative options. Video was resized 2x in Sony Vegas while preserving original aspect ratio. Original resolution is 720x576 interlaced. PAL exclusive title. Loading screen times have been reduced in editing.

Walkthrough Playthrough Gameplay Robin Hood's Quest Full Game Complete
